// src/pages/member/ExpensesPage.js import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import './ExpensesPage.css'; const MemberExpensesPage = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [stats, setStats] = useState({ monthlyContribution: 5000, totalPaid: 45000, pendingAmount: 5000, lastPaymentDate: '1/10/2025' }); const [expenses, setExpenses] = useState([]); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true); useEffect(() => { const mockExpenses = [ { id: 1, month: 'October 2025', amount: 5000, dueDate: '5/11/2025', status: 'paid', paymentDate: '1/10/2025', paymentMethod: 'Online Transfer', receipt: 'REC001' }, { id: 2, month: 'September 2025', amount: 5000, dueDate: '5/10/2025', status: 'paid', paymentDate: '2/9/2025', paymentMethod: 'Cheque', receipt: 'REC002' }, { id: 3, month: 'August 2025', amount: 5000, dueDate: '5/9/2025', status: 'paid', paymentDate: '1/8/2025', paymentMethod: 'Online Transfer', receipt: 'REC003' }, { id: 4, month: 'July 2025', amount: 5000, dueDate: '5/8/2025', status: 'paid', paymentDate: '3/7/2025', paymentMethod: 'Cash', receipt: 'REC004' }, { id: 5, month: 'June 2025', amount: 5000, dueDate: '5/7/2025', status: 'paid', paymentDate: '1/6/2025', paymentMethod: 'Online Transfer', receipt: 'REC005' } ]; setTimeout(() => { setExpenses(mockExpenses); setLoading(false); }, 1000); }, []); const handlePayNow = () => { alert('支付功能将在实际应用中实现'); }; const handleDownloadReceipt = (receipt) => { alert(`下载收据: ${receipt}`); }; const formatAmount = (amount) => { return new Intl.NumberFormat('en-IN', { style: 'currency', currency: 'INR', minimumFractionDigits: 0 }).format(amount); }; return (

My Expenses

View and manage your monthly contributions

{loading ? (
) : ( <>

{formatAmount(stats.monthlyContribution)}

Total Paid

{formatAmount(stats.totalPaid)}

Payment History

Month Amount Due Date Status Payment Date Payment Method Receipt Actions
{expense.month} {formatAmount(expense.amount)} {expense.dueDate} {expense.status.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + expense.status.slice(1)} {expense.paymentDate} {expense.paymentMethod} {expense.receipt}
)}
); }; export default MemberExpensesPage;
